ReflectionUtil - Class in net.amoebaman.utils.nms
Contains static methods useful for utilizing reflection as a workaround and alternative for directly importing NMS (net.minecraft.server) and OBC (org.bukkit.craftbukkit) classes, as plugins importing those classes will break with each update of Bukkit/CraftBukkit.
